<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.3">
<l>vēyiruñ cōlai vilaṅkal cūḻnta meyyama ṇāḷa rivvai yamellām</l>
<l>tāyiṉa nāya karāvar tōḻī tāmaraik kaṇka ḷirunta vāṟu</l>
<l>cēyiruṅ kuṉṟan tikaḻnta toppac cevviya vāki malarnta cōti</l>
<l>āyiran tōḷo ṭilaṅku pūṇu maccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Dear] friend, the groom of Meyyam, encircled by hills of vast bamboo groves,</l>
<l>Is the hero who crossed over all of this world. The way his lotus eyes are!</l>
<l>[He has] jewels that shine on his one-thousand arms</l>
<l rend="indent">whose light radiates elegantly,</l>
<l>Like they are shining on a distant dark mountain.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
